00:00:00.256 --> 00:00:04.352
<b>In Safety In Motion the first muscle to engage is your brain.</b>

00:00:04.864 --> 00:00:05.888
<b>Before you lift,</b>

00:00:06.144 --> 00:00:08.192
<b>take a moment to evaluate the load.</b>

00:00:08.704 --> 00:00:10.240
<b>How heavy is too heavy?</b>

00:00:10.752 --> 00:00:11.776
<b>Is it to big?</b>

00:00:12.288 --> 00:00:16.128
<b>Is it too hot or cold to lift and carry using good technique?</b>

00:00:16.640 --> 00:00:18.688
<b>Is it difficult to grip and hold?</b>

00:00:18.944 --> 00:00:20.992
<b>For example is the load slippery?</b>

00:00:21.504 --> 00:00:22.016
<b>Floppy?</b>

00:00:22.528 --> 00:00:23.040
<b>Sharp</b>

00:00:23.485 --> 00:00:24.504
<b>or in motion?</b>

